        <updateDate>2019-06-13T18:07:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Officers of the Law In Civilian Establishments Act of 2017 or the POLICE Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to modify the restriction on possessing a firearm or other dangerous weapon in a federal facility.</p> <p>Specifically, the prohibition does not apply to the lawful carrying of agency-issued firearms and dangerous weapons by a uniformed law enforcement officer in certain publicly accessible federal facilities.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
